Package: dotx
Version: 1.0.0
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 7), libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), libssl3 (>= 3.0.0)
Recommends: minimap2
Maintainer: DotX Development Team <contact@dotx.bio>
Homepage: https://github.com/dotx-bio/dotx
Description: Extreme-scale dot plot visualization for bioinformatics
 DotX is a revolutionary, offline, single-application dot-plot system that 
 scales to ~100 Gb per axis with near 1 bp/px zoom, powered by a sparse 
 multiresolution data model and optional GPU acceleration.
 .
 Features:
  * Extreme Scale: Browse 10ยนยน bp axes with smooth interaction
  * Cross-Platform: Windows, macOS, Linux support  
  * GPU Accelerated: Optional GPU processing for maximum performance
  * Deterministic: Exact reproducible results with embedded provenance
  * Offline-First: No internet required, no telemetry by default
 .
 This package includes both the GUI application and command-line interface.
